WEBVTT

00:01.967 --> 00:03.167
<i>Leonardo.</i>

00:03.235 --> 00:05.703
It speaks with
my mother's voice!

00:07.539 --> 00:09.140
Don't take the book away
from my people.

00:09.208 --> 00:10.808
There was no book.

00:12.177 --> 00:14.612
<i>Duke Federico</i>
<i>surrounds Florence.</i>

00:14.680 --> 00:17.181
Perhaps it is
time to strike.

00:17.249 --> 00:19.083
<i>Lorenzo di Medici.</i>

00:19.151 --> 00:22.353
What a priceless opportunity
to discuss your surrender.

00:23.589 --> 00:24.889
She was your mother.

00:24.957 --> 00:26.924
This is where faith
has carried me.

00:28.227 --> 00:29.694
What personal business would
the son of the Sultan

00:29.761 --> 00:32.563
have with the prized mistress
of Lorenzo di Medici,

00:32.631 --> 00:33.531
Signora Donati?

00:33.599 --> 00:36.067
You came here
expecting peace?

00:36.134 --> 00:38.102
Rid my house
of this filth.

00:38.170 --> 00:39.737
We shall soon know
the truth

00:39.805 --> 00:41.138
without laying a hand
upon you.

00:41.206 --> 00:42.874
How could that device
be built without

00:42.941 --> 00:44.842
the knowledge
of the Book of Leaves?

00:44.910 --> 00:48.212
Leo, it's a miracle!
The quest is far from over.

